item.title: Fallout TV show comes to Miniature world!
item.dc:creator: enriquegonzalezbabino@gmail.com
item.content:encoded: Dont miss it! Modiphius has created miniatures for Fallout: Wasteland Warfare and Fallout: Factions based on the main characters of the Amazon Prime Video Fallout TV series. Dubbed the Hollywood Heroes expansion, this bundle contains four 32mm unpainted minis modeled after the main characters of the show, including Lucy, Max, The Ghoul, and certified good boy, CX404. The $34.99 expansion doesn’t launch until May 7, but you can currently reserve your set from Amazon and Modiphius.

item.title: Privacy Policy
item.dc:creator: enriquegonzalezbabino@gmail.com
item.content:encoded:
Who we are

Suggested text: Our website address is: http://project-one.local.

Comments

Suggested text: When visitors leave comments on the site we collect the data shown in the comments form, and also the visitor’s IP address and browser user agent string to help spam detection.

An anonymized string created from your email address (also called a hash) may be provided to the Gravatar service to see if you are using it. The Gravatar service privacy policy is available here: https://automattic.com/privacy/. After approval of your comment, your profile picture is visible to the public in the context of your comment.

Media

Suggested text: If you upload images to the website, you should avoid uploading images with embedded location data (EXIF GPS) included. Visitors to the website can download and extract any location data from images on the website.

Cookies

Suggested text: If you leave a comment on our site you may opt-in to saving your name, email address and website in cookies. These are for your convenience so that you do not have to fill in your details again when you leave another comment. These cookies will last for one year.

If you visit our login page, we will set a temporary cookie to determine if your browser accepts cookies. This cookie contains no personal data and is discarded when you close your browser.

When you log in, we will also set up several cookies to save your login information and your screen display choices. Login cookies last for two days, and screen options cookies last for a year. If you select "Remember Me", your login will persist for two weeks. If you log out of your account, the login cookies will be removed.

If you edit or publish an article, an additional cookie will be saved in your browser. This cookie includes no personal data and simply indicates the post ID of the article you just edited. It expires after 1 day.

Embedded content from other websites

Suggested text: Articles on this site may include embedded content (e.g. videos, images, articles, etc.). Embedded content from other websites behaves in the exact same way as if the visitor has visited the other website.

These websites may collect data about you, use cookies, embed additional third-party tracking, and monitor your interaction with that embedded content, including tracking your interaction with the embedded content if you have an account and are logged in to that website.

Who we share your data with

Suggested text: If you request a password reset, your IP address will be included in the reset email.

How long we retain your data

Suggested text: If you leave a comment, the comment and its metadata are retained indefinitely. This is so we can recognize and approve any follow-up comments automatically instead of holding them in a moderation queue.

For users that register on our website (if any), we also store the personal information they provide in their user profile. All users can see, edit, or delete their personal information at any time (except they cannot change their username). Website administrators can also see and edit that information.

What rights you have over your data

Suggested text: If you have an account on this site, or have left comments, you can request to receive an exported file of the personal data we hold about you, including any data you have provided to us. You can also request that we erase any personal data we hold about you. This does not include any data we are obliged to keep for administrative, legal, or security purposes.

Where your data is sent

Suggested text: Visitor comments may be checked through an automated spam detection service.

item.title: Refund and Returns Policy
item.dc:creator: enriquegonzalezbabino@gmail.com
item.content:encoded:
This is a sample page.

Overview

Our refund and returns policy lasts 30 days. If 30 days have passed since your purchase, we can’t offer you a full refund or exchange.

To be eligible for a return, your item must be unused and in the same condition that you received it. It must also be in the original packaging.

Several types of goods are exempt from being returned. Perishable goods such as food, flowers, newspapers or magazines cannot be returned. We also do not accept products that are intimate or sanitary goods, hazardous materials, or flammable liquids or gases.

Additional non-returnable items:

  • Gift cards
  • Downloadable software products
  • Some health and personal care items

To complete your return, we require a receipt or proof of purchase.

Please do not send your purchase back to the manufacturer.

There are certain situations where only partial refunds are granted:

  • Book with obvious signs of use
  • CD, DVD, VHS tape, software, video game, cassette tape, or vinyl record that has been opened.
  • Any item not in its original condition, is damaged or missing parts for reasons not due to our error.
  • Any item that is returned more than 30 days after delivery

Refunds

Once your return is received and inspected, we will send you an email to notify you that we have received your returned item. We will also notify you of the approval or rejection of your refund.

If you are approved, then your refund will be processed, and a credit will automatically be applied to your credit card or original method of payment, within a certain amount of days.

Late or missing refunds

If you haven’t received a refund yet, first check your bank account again.

Then contact your credit card company, it may take some time before your refund is officially posted.

Next contact your bank. There is often some processing time before a refund is posted.

If you’ve done all of this and you still have not received your refund yet, please contact us at {email address}.

Sale items

Only regular priced items may be refunded. Sale items cannot be refunded.

Exchanges

We only replace items if they are defective or damaged. If you need to exchange it for the same item, send us an email at {email address} and send your item to: {physical address}.

Gifts

If the item was marked as a gift when purchased and shipped directly to you, you’ll receive a gift credit for the value of your return. Once the returned item is received, a gift certificate will be mailed to you.

If the item wasn’t marked as a gift when purchased, or the gift giver had the order shipped to themselves to give to you later, we will send a refund to the gift giver and they will find out about your return.

Shipping returns

To return your product, you should mail your product to: {physical address}.

You will be responsible for paying for your own shipping costs for returning your item. Shipping costs are non-refundable. If you receive a refund, the cost of return shipping will be deducted from your refund.

Depending on where you live, the time it may take for your exchanged product to reach you may vary.

If you are returning more expensive items, you may consider using a trackable shipping service or purchasing shipping insurance. We don’t guarantee that we will receive your returned item.

Need help?

Contact us at {email} for questions related to refunds and returns.

item.title: Plydolex Wooden Paint Organizer
item.dc:creator: enriquegonzalezbabino@gmail.com
item.content:encoded:
Keep Your Colors in Perfect Order Introducing the Plydolex Wooden Paint Organizer, the ultimate solution for organizing your miniature paint collection. Crafted with precision from high-quality wood, this organizer is designed to keep your paints neatly arranged and easily accessible, so you can focus on what matters most—unleashing your creativity. Features:
  • Sturdy Construction: Made from durable wood, the Plydolex Organizer ensures long-lasting reliability and stability, keeping your paints secure and steady.
  • Ample Storage: With multiple compartments and slots, this organizer offers generous storage space for a variety of paint bottles, ensuring every color in your collection has its place.
  • Compact Design: Despite its spacious interior, the Plydolex Organizer maintains a compact footprint, making it ideal for any workspace—whether it's a dedicated studio or a cozy corner of your home.
  • Easy Access: The slanted design allows for easy viewing and access to your paints, so you can quickly find the perfect shade without rummaging through cluttered drawers or shelves.

item.title: Wet Palette for Painting Kit.
item.dc:creator: enriquegonzalezbabino@gmail.com
item.content:encoded:
Unleash Your Painting Potential with Precision and Perfection Introducing the Wet Palette for Painting Kit, the essential tool for every miniature artist seeking unparalleled control and seamless blending in their work. Designed with precision and functionality in mind, this kit revolutionizes your painting experience, allowing you to achieve stunning results with ease. Features:
  • Optimal Moisture Control: The wet palette maintains the perfect level of moisture to keep your paints workable for hours, preventing them from drying out and allowing for seamless blending and layering.
  • Durable Construction: Crafted from high-quality materials, the wet palette is built to last, providing a reliable and sturdy surface for your painting sessions.
  • Generous Mixing Area: With a spacious mixing surface, the wet palette allows you to experiment with color combinations and create custom shades with ease.
  • Portable Design: Compact and lightweight, the kit is easy to transport, making it ideal for painting on the go or taking to workshops and events.

item.title: Vallejo Paint Set: "Master's Palette Collection"
item.dc:creator: enriquegonzalezbabino@gmail.com
item.content:encoded:
Unleash Your Creativity with Vallejo's Master's Palette Collection Experience the unparalleled quality and versatility of Vallejo paints with the Master's Palette Collection. This comprehensive set includes a curated selection of premium acrylic paints, carefully chosen to meet the needs of both beginner and advanced miniature painters alike. Features:
  • Wide Range of Colors: From vibrant primaries to subtle neutrals, the Master's Palette Collection offers a diverse range of colors to bring your miniatures to life.
  • High Pigment Density: Vallejo paints are renowned for their rich, opaque coverage and smooth consistency, ensuring excellent color saturation and blending capabilities.
  • Airbrush Compatible: These acrylic paints are formulated for use with both brush and airbrush techniques, providing flexibility and versatility in your painting process.
  • Dropper Bottle Design: Each paint comes in a convenient dropper bottle, allowing for precise dispensing and minimal waste.

item.title: Army Painter Paint Set: "Battlefield Essentials Collection"
item.dc:creator: enriquegonzalezbabino@gmail.com
item.content:encoded:
Conquer Your Painting Battles with the Army Painter's Battlefield Essentials Collection Prepare for war and paint your army to victory with the Battlefield Essentials Collection from the Army Painter. This meticulously curated set contains a range of high-quality paints specifically designed for wargaming miniatures, ensuring that every soldier in your army looks their best on the battlefield. Features:
  • Military-Grade Pigments: The Battlefield Essentials Collection features colors specially formulated for wargaming miniatures, with high pigment density and excellent coverage for easy application.
  • Quick-Drying Formula: Army Painter paints dry quickly to a matte finish, allowing you to quickly layer and highlight your miniatures without waiting for paint to dry.
  • Color-Coded Caps: Each paint pot is color-coded for easy identification, making it simple to find the perfect shade for your next project.
  • Includes Essential Tools: In addition to paints, this set includes essential tools such as a brush and a painting guide to help you get started on your miniature painting journey.

item.title: Gnome Sweet Gnome – the Community-Painted New Blood Bowl Gnomes Are Looking Fine
item.dc:creator: enriquegonzalezbabino@gmail.com
item.content:encoded: Check It Out! The Glimdarrow Groundhogs took us all by surprise when they scampered from their enchanted forest and arrived ready to tussle on the astrogranite. As you can imagine, they’ve captured the hearts and minds of the community, who have submitted some fabulous paintwork. We begin with Chris Lewis, whose Rodney Roachbait and Treeman are painted in vibrant red, blue, and green. The new Treeman in particular looks very hard to put down.

item.title: Citadel Paint Set: "Fantasy Color Collection"
item.dc:creator: enriquegonzalezbabino@gmail.com
item.content:encoded:
Embark on a Colorful Journey with the Citadel Fantasy Color Collection Enter the fantastical world of miniature painting with the Citadel Fantasy Color Collection. Developed by Games Workshop, Citadel paints are renowned for their vibrant colors, smooth application, and unparalleled quality, making them the perfect choice for painting your favorite fantasy miniatures. Features:
  • Fantasy-Inspired Shades: From bold, otherworldly hues to subtle, earthy tones, the Fantasy Color Collection offers a diverse range of colors inspired by the realms of fantasy.
  • Layering and Blending Capabilities: Citadel paints are formulated for easy layering and blending, allowing you to achieve smooth transitions and stunning visual effects on your miniatures.
  • Specialized Formulas: With specialized formulas for base, layer, shade, and technical paints, Citadel offers everything you need to bring your fantasy creations to life with precision and detail.
  • Officially Licensed: As the official paint range of Games Workshop, Citadel paints are designed to complement their range of miniatures, ensuring seamless compatibility and stunning results.
